STATE of New Jersey, Plaintiff-Respondent,
v.
Mark GREEN, a/k/a Mark Scott, Alton Green, Altur Green and Anton Green, Defendant-Petitioner. 079752
C-121 Sept. Term 2017 Supreme Court of New Jersey. September 28, 2017

ON PETITION FOR CERTIFICATION.

To the Appellate Division, Superior Court:

A petition for certification of the judgment in A-001938-15 having been submitted to this Court, and the Court having considered the same;

It is ORDERED that the petition for certification is denied.
